  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个工作流图，描述从启动到结束的完整流程。起点是一个特殊的开始节点，终点是结束节点。中间有三个主要处理环节：提取关键词、文件处理，还有一个websearch模块。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "__start__",
        "__end__",
        "extract_keywords",
        "file_process",
        "websearch"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。我注意到您提到了generate这个环节，它应该放在什么位置？是独立的处理节点吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "generate"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，generate是关键输出节点。流程是这样：开始之后可以并行触发提取关键词、文件处理和generate。但websearch必须在提取关键词之后才能执行，然后websearch的结果要喂给generate。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "__start__",
        "extract_keywords",
        "file_process",
        "generate",
        "websearch"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "文件处理和提取关键词的关系呢？看起来文件处理完成后也要走提取关键词？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "file_process",
        "extract_keywords"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，文件处理完要进入提取关键词。所以提取关键词有两个入口：直接从开始节点过来，或者从文件处理过来。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "file_process",
        "extract_keywords",
        "__start__"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先搭建整体结构。开始节点用圆形，结束节点也用圆形，中间四个处理节点用矩形。开始节点到提取关键词、文件处理、generate都用虚线连接，表示并行触发。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "__start__",
        "extract_keywords",
        "file_process",
        "generate"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "视觉样式上，开始节点我想做成透明的，完全不填充，这样比较符合惯例。结束节点用淡紫色填充，和中间节点区分开。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "__start__",
        "__end__"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "收到，开始节点fill-opacity设0，结束节点用#bfb6fc。那提取关键词到websearch，以及websearch到generate的连接，我也用虚线吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "extract_keywords",
        "websearch",
        "generate"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "不对，websearch到generate应该用实线，这是强依赖关系。但提取关键词到websearch可以保持虚线。另外文件处理到提取关键词必须是实线，这是顺序执行。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "file_process",
        "extract_keywords",
        "websearch",
        "generate"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "调整好了。文件处理→提取关键词实线，提取关键词→websearch虚线，websearch→generate实线。generate到结束节点也用实线。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "file_process",
        "extract_keywords",
        "websearch",
        "generate",
        "__end__"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "提取关键词到generate也是虚线对吧？表示它可以不经过websearch直接触发生成？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "extract_keywords",
        "generate"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，保留虚线连接。所有节点默认用浅紫色背景，行高1.2。曲线样式用linear直线，这样流程图更清晰。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "extract_keywords",
        "generate"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完美，这个结构准确反映了我们的业务逻辑。开始节点透明，结束节点深紫，中间流程一目了然。",
